uk.ac.man.jb.pct.data
Interface I_DataFileParser

All Known Implementing Classes:
PatternFileProcessor
public interface I_DataFileParser

I_DataFileParser, defines an interface specifying the methods needed to read the data files used by the application.

Author:
Rob Lyon
